 to the local [CII]-SFR relation; however, its\nluminosity is consistent with upper limits derived for most $z\\sim6$ galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2016 20:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2016 14:52:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-25"}
