e the DMM prediction matches the data well. The\nfull-dispersion DMM is also found to closely predict the experimentally\nobserved temperature-dependent interface conductance for epitaxial NiSi/Si and\nnon-epitaxial TiSi$_2$/Si interfaces. In the case of epitaxial PtSi/Si\ninterfaces, full dispersion DMM significantly overpredicts the experimental\ndata.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2016 22:04:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2016 20:48:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2017 16:53:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-01"}
