on\nfor the normalized volumes of the corresponding polytopes via the hook formula.\nFinally, Stanley's theory of $(P,\\omega)$-partitions allows us to show that\ntheir $h^*$-vectors are symmetric and unimodal.\n  Various questions and conjectures are presented throughout.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2016 22:50:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Jun 2017 20:50:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Jul 2018 14:48:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-18"}
